  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>TitTok - Minimalistic adventure 2D puzzle platformer with cats, explosions and spinning saws!</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534260/extras/73481f72bd20afaf304c88c343a1bb88.poster.avif?t=1773984727\" width=544 height=152 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534260/extras/73481f72bd20afaf304c88c343a1bb88.webm?t=1773984727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534260/extras/73481f72bd20afaf304c88c343a1bb88.mp4?t=1773984727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>The player's goal is to complete all levels and not die from the attacks of evil enemies.<br>You can find bombs in the levels and use them anywhere!</i><br><br>▪ Kitties ^. ^<br>▪ 31 levels;<br>▪ Platformer levels;<br>▪ Levels with puzzles;<br>▪ Diverse and evil enemies;<br>▪ Spinning deadly saws;<br>▪ Bombs and explosions;<br>▪ Destruction;<br>▪ Double jumps;<br>▪ Portals;<br>▪ Mask mode;<br>▪ Leaderboards and statistics;<br>▪ 69 Achievements;<br>▪ Boss Helicopter!<br><br><strong>...And in the game you can MEOW at any time ^^</strong><br><strong>TikTok? No! TitTok! TikTok ≠ TitTok</strong><br><strong>And remember: \"Tit before your Tok!\"</strong>",
